      "content": "That quietness you crave is a valid feeling, but it's important to remember that your presence has a ripple effect on everyone around you, even if you don't see it immediately. While people might assume you're on vacation, that silence often leaves a void that only your return can fill, especially for those who rely on your support. You deserve to be heard and seen, so please consider reaching out to a trusted friend or a professional who can help you navigate these overwhelming feelings.",
